    "name": "Crisol: Theater of Idols",
    "steam_appid": 1790930,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《炼魂之地：神偶剧院》是一款扣人心弦的第一人称恐怖动作冒险游戏，在这令人毛骨悚然的希斯帕尼亚世界中，重塑西班牙之梦魇。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >玩家将扮演加布里埃尔，一位能将自身鲜血化为致命武器的士兵，踏上完成太阳神赋予的神圣使命的旅程。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏特色：</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1790930/extras/241c4395c02adc5b451d99efe6ef78db.poster.avif?t=1771614740\" width=720 height=480 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1790930/extras/241c4395c02adc5b451d99efe6ef78db.webm?t=1771614740\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>探索受诅之岛“托门托萨”</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >踏上托门托萨这座美丽却邪恶的岛屿，揭开它那令人胆寒的过往和扭曲不堪的传说。周遭环境阴森可怖，你将目睹破败的宏伟遗迹，穿过纵横交错的街道，掀起邪教和血祭的层层面纱。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1790930/extras/c31628b76a793d399141aed00b431d0a.poster.avif?t=1771614740\" width=720 height=480 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1790930/extras/c31628b76a793d399141aed00b431d0a.webm?t=1771614740\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>血为利器，亦是诅咒</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >鲜血既是你的生命之源，也是你的歼敌杀器。请善用这一新掌握的力量，借之对抗可怕敌人、解决复杂谜题。但要小心：每次射击都会消耗你的生命，所以，三思而后行。你能否存续于世，将取决于自身平衡生死的能力。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1790930/extras/ad5ba06293a5bbc15eb477362032bb36.poster.avif?t=1771614740\" width=720 height=480 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1790930/extras/ad5ba06293a5bbc15eb477362032bb36.webm?t=1771614740\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>掌管你的力量与武器</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >强化力量，提升血液致命性，让你能够持久作战的同时伤害高涨，亦可在战斗中获取助战增益。探索托门托萨岛，利用寻得的金币调试各类武器，以此适应不同战斗局势，并逐步加以改进。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1790930/extras/111384ac2b70ed95d58b4be53393c258.poster.avif?t=1771614740\" width=720 height=480 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1790930/extras/111384ac2b70ed95d58b4be53393c258.webm?t=1771614740\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>源于历史、恐怖四溢的故事</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >发生在希斯帕尼亚半岛的历史事件、民间传说和宗教底蕴交相融合，并铸造出如此一个独特的恐怖世界。去直面那些被赋予生命的巨大雕像，解开一个现实与梦魇交织缠绕的暗黑故事吧。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >准备好牺牲一切吧。走上这趟“求真之路”，你又愿意流多少血？  </p>",
